- **Base domain** (e.g., `securehero.com`) â†’ English by default
- **Czech domain** (e.g., `securehero.com/cz`) â†’ Czech content
- **IP-based detection** â†’ auto-redirect to `/cz` for Czech IPs
- **Manual switcher** â†’ user can override language preference

